                    <div class="max-w-lg">                        
                        <h1 class="mt-10 text-3xl font-light font-lato tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
                            We <strong>build</strong> innovative digital <strong>experiences</strong> by combining <strong>AI, design</strong> and <strong>technology</strong>.
